item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Network_Bandwidth_Version1_Usage
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Network_Bandwidth_Version1_Usage Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Network_Bandwidth_Version1_Usage models an hourly bandwidth record. Local incomingAmount The amount of incoming bandwidth that a server has used within the hour of the recordedDate. Type: float outgoingAmount The amount of outgoing bandwidth that a server has used within the hour of the recordedDate. Type: float recordedDate The date and time that the bandwidth was used by a piece of hardware Type: dateTime
